These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, april, december
City: boston, liverpool, nizza, colone
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to nizza##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | december | february     | april | august |
| City     | boston     | nizza | colone  | liverpool      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, bellflower, zinnia, marigold
City: edinburgh, boston, london, san-francisco
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Flower   | dahlia | bellflower    | marigold     | zinnia  |
| City     | edinburgh    | london | boston | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, october, may
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, taxi, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | april   | october   | december  | may |
| Transport           | jet-ski | snowmobile | taxi | bike  |

