.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
House: cottage, art-deco, townhouse, colonial
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, scientific, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the colonial house is between the cottage house and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the colonial house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
5. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| House         | art-deco | cottage | colonial | townhouse  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | zombie   | epic  | scientific |

