.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, swimming, golf, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, motorbike, helicopter
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | tennis    | swimming   | golf | rugby    |
| Transport      | taxi | quad-bike | motorbike       | helicopter |

