.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, canasta, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, baking, drawing, hiking
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person playing canasta##2
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person playing whist##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Game    | whist | canasta | snooker | monopoly |
| Hobby   | baking | dancing  | drawing    | hiking  |

