.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dannemann, old-henry, prince
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, adventure, documentary, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the prince-smoker##2
5. the person watching adventure movies is the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | prince | old-henry | dannemann     |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | epic  | adventure   | documentary |

