.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, backgammon, domino
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing domino is the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Game         | domino | backgammon | monopoly | canasta   |
| Flower   | marigold | amaryllis | tulip      | azalea |

