.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, security-guard, librarian, accountant
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, ivory, blood-red, red
1. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes red is the accountant##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the security-guard##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the security-guard is between the person who likes ivory and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job     | lawyer | security-guard   | librarian      | accountant      |
| Color   | ivory     | blood-red | blue | red |

