.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, drama, scientific
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, mouse, rabbit
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | horror | drama      | scientific   |
| Pet   | mouse  | rat    | lizard | rabbit |

