.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, sunflower, balloon-flower
There 4 different types of food: radish, cauliflower, papaya, lettuce
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person eating lettuce is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
6. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower       | lily | sunflower | balloon-flower    | daisy      |
| Food   | papaya       | lettuce       | cauliflower | radish |

