4. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Color   | ivory     | aquamarine  | black | fuchsia |
| Job     | librarian | freelancer | analyst     | nurse    |

