.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, coffee, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, amaryllis, marigold
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | coffee  | water | soy-milk |
| Flower           | amaryllis     | marigold | dahlia    | rose     |

