.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, mexican, russian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, blend, chaman, oliveros
1. the russian is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Nationality   | dutch  | british | russian  | mexican      |
| Cigar    | oliveros | fonseca | chaman | blend |

