.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
House: modern, cape-cod, gothic-revival, ranch-style
City: marseilles, edinburgh, liverpool, colone
1. the modern house is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the modern house##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| House         | cape-cod | ranch-style | gothic-revival | modern |
| City   | colone     | marseilles       | edinburgh   | liverpool      |

