.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, chess, writing, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, funk, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | fishing | camping | writing | chess |
| Music-Genre         | salsa  | funk   | house | r&b     |

