.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, golf, cycling, cricket
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, lavender, aquamarine, blood-red
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Sport      | swimming | golf    | cricket  | cycling |
| Color   | chestnut       | lavender | aquamarine | blood-red  |

