.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, water, lemonade
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, canasta, chess
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking tea is the person playing chess##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing canasta is between the person drinking lemonade and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Beverage   | water | tea  | coffee  | lemonade |
| Game           | poker    | chess | canasta | backgammon |

