.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, van, car, boat
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, chess, go
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Transport   | boat        | tram       | car   | van |
| Game    | go | chess | mah-jongg | scrabble  |

