.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, colombian, thai, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, quad-bike, bus
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
3. the australian is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
4. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the french##1
7. the thai is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Nationality   | colombian     | french     | thai          | australian |
| Transport      | train | trike | bus | quad-bike  |

 